name: react-best-practices.mdc
description: Best practices for React component development and state management
globs: **/*.{ts,tsx}

- Use functional components with hooks instead of class components.
- Implement proper prop type checking with TypeScript interfaces.
- Utilize React.memo for performance optimization of functional components.
- Use custom hooks for reusable state logic and side effects.
- Implement state management with Zustand or TanStack React Query for global state and data fetching.